Refactoring into three separate gradle projects
We keep one core project which contains no implementation, but just interfaces.
One project which contains an iRODS implementation. Along with an additional project that potentially could use a more direct connection to our storage services.
Added a cleaner definition of pathsˆ
Some initial work for cleaning up in iRODS user definition
iRODS file tests and logging configuration
